author: Warhammer
description:
Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun 2 adds a second playable character!

Find out more about the battle-hardened Nyra Veyrath, a veteran Sister of Battle, and her arsenal inthis extended reveal trailer!

Find out more and wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3115160/Warhammer_40000_Boltgun_2/

Warhammer 40,000 Boltgun 2 is coming to PC, PS5 & Xbox Series X|S in 2026.
